/**

 * @title MPSSaleConfig

 * @dev MPSSaleConfig contract

 * The contract configure the sale for the MPS token

 *

 * @author Cyril Lapinte - <[email protected]>

 *

 * @notice Copyright © 2016 - 2018 Mt Pelerin Group SA - All Rights Reserved

